snippet.title: The Strike: Championship Edition - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: The #1 fishing game is coming to Nintendo Switch on October 23rd!  Fish for real with precise Nintendo Switch motion controls, or take it to the next level with the Power Cast Rod & Reel Peripheral to cast, jig, and reel your way to the championship!
